### Component 4: Engine Detection — `script_creation_tab.py`

#### [MODIFY] [script_creation_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/script_creation_tab.py)

**4A. Config-driven phase plan detection:**
```python
# Parse pipeline_features từ style_json_raw
_style_data = json.loads(style_json_raw)
_pipeline_features = _style_data.get("pipeline_features", {})
_has_phase_plan = _pipeline_features.get("phase_plan", False)

# Backward compat CHỈ cho biography styles cũ (chưa có pipeline_features)
if not _has_phase_plan:
    _BIO_KW = ("biography", "tiểu sử", "nhân vật", "chân dung", "cuộc đời")
    _has_phase_plan = any(kw in (niche or "").lower() for kw in _BIO_KW)
    if _has_phase_plan:
        _pipeline_features = {
            "phase_plan": True, "validate_sub_keys": True,
            "split_threshold": [3, 6],
            "always_include_keys": ["core_identity", "personal_profile"],
            "excerpt_fields": ["life_phases", "turning_points", "conflicts"],
        }
```

