## Error Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Pipeline Start] --> B{style has pipeline_features.phase_plan?}
    B -->|No + not biography| C[Skip Step A — single-shot outline]
    B -->|Yes| D[Step A1: Phase Plan]
    
    D --> D1{phase_plan prompt exists for niche?}
    D1 -->|No| ERR1["❌ RuntimeError: No phase_plan prompt"]
    D1 -->|Yes| D2[AI classifies main/sub via 2-tier filter]
    
    D2 --> E[Step A2: Validate Sub-keys]
    E --> E1{validate_sub_key prompt exists?}
    E1 -->|No| ERR2["❌ RuntimeError: No validate prompt"]
    E1 -->|Yes| E2{excerpt_fields configured?}
    E2 -->|No| ERR3["❌ RuntimeError: excerpt_fields missing"]
    E2 -->|Yes| E3{blueprint has excerpt_fields?}
    E3 -->|No| ERR4["❌ RuntimeError: Blueprint schema mismatch"]
    E3 -->|Yes| E4[3-Test Promote — adapted per niche]
    
    E4 --> F[Step A3: Apply Splits — configurable threshold]
    F --> G[Step B: Outline]
    G --> H[Step C: Audit]
    H --> I[Step D: Write Chapters]
    
    I --> I1{always_include_keys in blueprint?}
    I1 -->|No| ERR5["❌ RuntimeError: Missing always-keys"]
    I1 -->|Yes| I2{key_data matched blueprint?}
    I2 -->|No| ERR6["❌ RuntimeError: key_data mismatch"]
    I2 -->|Yes| I3[Write with filtered blueprint]
    
